Next.js app 

1. Install it : 

npm install --save next react react-dom

2. Add script : 

{
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "next",
    "build": "next build",
    "start": "next start"
  }
}

3. Populate page ./pages/index.js

export default () => <div>Welcome to next.js!</div>

4. Run "npm run dev"

5. http://localhost:3000
